1. Cathie Wood: Bitcoin holders may transfer BTC to Coinbase for mortgage loans to buy houses;
2. LeverFi has issued about 13.7 billion LEVER tokens, some of which have been recharged to exchanges;
3. Data: BlackRock has increased its holdings of BTC for nine consecutive weeks, with a total increase of about 107,139;
4. Chairman of the US Digital Asset Financial Advisory Committee: The proportion of cryptocurrency portfolios can be increased to 10-40%;
5. The number of warning letters issued by the IRS to crypto investors has surged by more than 750% in the past 60 days, and the new tax regulations have caused concerns;
6. Report: Most Bitcoin reserve strategy companies may fall into a "death spiral", and only a few can survive;
7. REX Shares: Solana pledged ETF is about to be launched.
